Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:34.63,OPC,,0,0,0,,Spark me up! check check check!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:38.57,OPC,,0,0,0,,未能满足 想被看透
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:42.60,OPC,,0,0,0,,想把这份感情变成蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:46.72,OPC,,0,0,0,,想更深入 已经按耐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:50.35,OPC,,0,0,0,,希望得到上天的启示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:52.50,OPC,,0,0,0,,无需搅乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:54.44,OPC,,0,0,0,,一直当个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.47,0:00:56.54,OPC,,0,0,0,,妄想的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:58.51,OPC,,0,0,0,,不会崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:00.50,OPC,,0,0,0,,虽想要呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:02.47,OPC,,0,0,0,,然而微弱的叹息中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.46,OPC,,0,0,0,,咒语并未起效
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:07.80,OPC,,0,0,0,,（Go ready Go）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:10.58,OPC,,0,0,0,,今天来一场赌博吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:14.03,OPC,,0,0,0,,陷入听天由命的未知中 (Go baby NEW-NEW)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.03,0:01:16.48,OPC,,0,0,0,,度过吧 (Go,baby NEW-WAY NEW-WAY)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:18.53,OPC,,0,0,0,,变得狂野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:21.90,OPC,,0,0,0,,向着恋爱的秘境 (Go baby NEW-NEW)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:24.54,OPC,,0,0,0,,进发 (Go,baby NEW-WAY NEW-WAY)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:26.57,OPC,,0,0,0,,黄昏之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.99,OPC,,0,0,0,,不管何事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:33.55,OPC,,0,0,0,,都让我们在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:35.56,OPC,,0,0,0,,NOW·NOW·NOW·NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:37.57,OPC,,0,0,0,,NEW·NEW·NEW·NEW
